          "<span class='font-bold text-blue-600'> Coming soon: Ring A1 - Cattle </a></span><br/>Results for the Cattle classes in Ring A1",
        icon: 'flat-color-icons:template',
      },
      {
        title: '2025 Ovine Results:',
